### üõí Products

### 1. Get All Products (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products

### 2. Search Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?search=apple

### 3. Filter by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?category=Dairy

### 4. Search and Sort by Price (Low to High)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?category=Fruits&sort=price

### 5. Filter by Price Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?minPrice=10&maxPrice=100&sort=-createdAt

### 6. Create a Product (Requires Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Test Product",
    "description": "This is a test product",
    "price": 99,
    "category": "Organic",
    "stock": 10,
    "location": "Meerut"
}

